                <note rend="inline" type="source">894A.00/6–1749: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul General at Tientsin</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Tientsin</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-06-23T20:00:00-04:00"
                            >June 23, 1949—8 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>157. While appreciating force of argument ur 430 June 7 [<hi rend="italic"
                        >21</hi>], Dept believes public statement re Formosa unwise at this
                    time.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
